data.description: Beautiful Home in the lovely Yucatan del Este neighborhood. This energy efficient, green built, Silver Level home features 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bath, and fully landscaped yard! The kitchen opens up to the family room and outdoor patio and features granite countertops and beautiful backsplash. Primary bedroom suite has large walk in closet, bathroom with double sink and separate shower and garden tub. Don't miss out on the opportunity to this in this sought after Rio Rancho neighborhood that in conveniently located to shopping, schools, and parks!
